<br>
Somehow I doubt software/MP3 thieves are into reading license agreements.  <img src=http://www.geocities.com/lag999/rolleyes.txt>  I do consider this whole issue to be a good demonstration of karma in action.  <img src=http://www.geocities.com/lag999/biggrin.txt><br>
<br>
In fact, the press Kazaa has received recently about this "feature" is more media hype than substance.  Any file stealing (sharing) program like Kazaa inherently poses a huge security risk for the user, even if it doesn't have any so-called "hidden networks".  Don't think that by following some instructions in an article you are making your computer any safer in reality. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usaliciaswiftfoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Salicia Swiftfoot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dragonlady of the Grove<br>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/4/02 9:36:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneralot.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1338.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://divineguildpics.homestead.com/files/natural.jpg height=138 width=85></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kazaa users - read this</span><hr size=1> Well Tuda, I agree with you... I pay for my software (well, I use my work software for home reasons at times, but the program never leaves the work computer :p) and I really do think filesharing is what's going to cost us all a lot more money in the future....  I only posted that because I saw Cobyll talking about Kazaa... <p><table><tr><td height=1 width=1 border=0 valign=bottom align=left><img src=http://divineguildpics.homestead.com/files/Salstamp.jpg height=100 width=50 border=0><td valign=bottom><font size=1>
